Text: The most amusing part about choosing racism as one's particular brand of batshit insanity is that it's so masochistic. Not that there ever was any such thing as "racial purity", but choosing to fight that battle is just buying a ticket on the Titanic and whining like a little bitch as it sinks.

George Lincoln Rockwell was a well documented fan of homosexual males.  

You're not hiding something too, are you Flakey?  Maybe just overcompensating?  Just be gay dude, nobody cares if you like the cocks.

Shalom.
